{"id":61261,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/网络“论坛死”，做鬼也风流！/","date":"2010-04-22T07:58:44Z","modified":"2010-04-22T07:58:44Z","title":"网络“论坛死”，做鬼也风流！","content":"<p><span>我不知道论坛是为物业管理公司说话，还是为业主说话，</span>    <br /><span>我真的不明白。</span>     <br />……………………………………………..</p>\n<p> <a href=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/3.jpg\"><img alt=\"3\" border=\"0\" height=\"264\" src=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/3_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width:0px;display:inline;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px\" title=\"3\" width=\"339\"></a> </p>\n<p><span>在</span>1<span>论坛发“网民案”、“疫苗案”、“玉树地震贴”，</span>    <br /><span>我的论坛</span>ID<span>：推特武士</span> <span>昨夜被永久禁止登陆，</span></p>\n<p><span>感谢国家</span> <span>感谢政府</span> <span>感谢党！</span>    <br /><span>让我有机会“论坛死”</span>,     <br /><span>能在</span>19<span>楼论坛骄傲的活着、有尊严的死去。</span> </p>\n<p><span>“推特武士”在论坛的网络生命刚满</span>60<span>天，</span>    <br /><span>因发布“网民案、疫苗案、地震案”，</span>     <br /><span>被论坛无声无息的关进论坛黑监狱，</span>     <br /><span>判处无期徒刑，</span>     <br /><span>剥夺政治权利、</span>     <br /><span>言论自由权利终生。</span> </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/4.jpg\"><img alt=\"4\" border=\"0\" height=\"257\" src=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/4_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width:0px;display:inline;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px\" title=\"4\" width=\"384\"></a> </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/5.jpg\"><img alt=\"5\" border=\"0\" height=\"244\" src=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/5_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width:0px;display:inline;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px\" title=\"5\" width=\"386\"></a> </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/6.jpg\"><img alt=\"6\" border=\"0\" height=\"322\" src=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/6_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width:0px;display:inline;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px\" title=\"6\" width=\"391\"></a> </p>\n<p><span>在论坛二个月，</span>    <br /><span>我很荣幸，</span>     <br /><span>自己没有说谎，</span>     <br /><span>没有欺骗，</span>     <br /><span>我只是说出了看见、听见的声音，</span>     <br /><span>我只是做一个公民可以做的事情，</span> </p>\n<p><span>爱国不等于爱朝廷，</span>    <br /><span>爱国不等于爱官府，</span>     <br /><span>如同美国人爱美国不等于爱奥巴马。</span> </p>\n<p><span>政府同国民的关系是物业公司也业主的关系，</span>    <br /><span>政府是十三亿中国城业主雇佣的物业管理公司，</span>     <br /><span>国家主席相当于物业管理公司的法人代表，</span>     <br /><span>我们纳税相当于交纳物业管理费养活物业管理公司，</span>     <br /><span>我们不需要感谢谁。</span> </p>\n<p><span>物业管理公司不能代表国家，</span>    <br /><span>物业公司法人代表也不能代表国家，</span>     <br /><span>顶多算个</span>CEO<span>。</span> </p>\n<p><span>网络不是虚拟社会，</span>    <br /><span>网络就是社会，</span> </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/2.jpg\"><img alt=\"2\" border=\"0\" height=\"302\" src=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/2_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width:0px;display:inline;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px\" title=\"2\" width=\"435\"></a></p>\n<p><span>网络是我遭遇的“论坛黑监狱”，</span>    <br /><span>如同福建网民为死者申冤遭遇的牢狱之灾。</span>     <br /><span>他们的命运就是你我的命运！</span> </p>\n<p><span>“推特武士”在中国的网络江湖出生入死只有两个月，</span>    <br /><span>今夜在论坛将化身为“推特骑士”，</span>     <br /><span>继续推特。</span> </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/1.jpg\"><img alt=\"1\" border=\"0\" height=\"341\" src=\"http://www.daxa.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/1_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width:0px;display:inline;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px\" title=\"1\" width=\"425\"></a> </p>\n<p><span>我轻轻的走了，</span>    <br /><span>正如我轻轻的来，</span>     <br /><span>换一个</span>ID<span>，</span>     <br /><span>不带走一片云彩。</span></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[9067,9212,14602]}